    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >控制强大的机器</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/8d9a24fd5fc815b03479cc14d9bfecd9.webp?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/146bff3c7f2b921d8422d7a08f7caecd.poster.avif?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/146bff3c7f2b921d8422d7a08f7caecd.webm?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/146bff3c7f2b921d8422d7a08f7caecd.mp4?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个名为HIVE的邪恶人工智能获得了自我意识，并征服了X星球！现在，由你来反击，使用各种车辆。从小巧快速的武装送货车到建筑物大小的重型机甲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完成任务和与不断增强的敌对机器的斗争，解锁新的车辆和武器。给你的车辆装备更新、更强大的武器。并利用强大的能力，比如迫击炮打击，当你的武器单独无法阻止无尽的杀手机器人潮时。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁毁灭性的武器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/03e0c3fbd66a28d2f3e19b320d0c863e.webp?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/497930f31dcce25fd3b545dc37d9582b.poster.avif?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/497930f31dcce25fd3b545dc37d9582b.webm?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/497930f31dcce25fd3b545dc37d9582b.mp4?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投资解锁高科技设备，例如激光、轨道炮和实验性机甲。或者全力投入导弹轰炸和重型坦克。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >科技树分为五个级别，每个级别的破坏力都比上一个更强。每项新研究将为你提供一种独特的方式来摧毁你的敌人和你路上的任何潜在建筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与成群的敌人作斗争</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/b58f8bfef6f421db8dd308968108eead.webp?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/615c3ada270e0c3974eaa59b6085338a.poster.avif?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/615c3ada270e0c3974eaa59b6085338a.webm?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/615c3ada270e0c3974eaa59b6085338a.mp4?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight various attacking automatons. Each has its own unique pros and cons for you to take advantage of. Use your flamethrower to take on swarms of self-destructing drones, or mobilize heavy weaponry to destroy threatening machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支援能力</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/98c5c773b68d72517a0ed848525ea379.webp?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/25f1ef66949f7e130831cde75cabbd80.poster.avif?t=1770722864\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/25f1ef66949f7e130831cde75cabbd80.webm?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237920/extras/25f1ef66949f7e130831cde75cabbd80.mp4?t=1770722864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用可部署炮塔！或者请求毁灭性的炮火打击！在正确的时机使用这些能力，将在你与可怕的杀手机器人群体的战斗中起到决定性作用！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制30多种不同的车辆，包括机甲、坦克和汽车。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制100多种武器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用强大的支援能力，例如炮火打击和可部署炮塔。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败三个不同的敌方子派系，每个子派系都有其独特的单位和环境。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在X星球上战斗，环境从沙丘到冰冻荒原，从森林到巨型城市。</p></li></ul>",
